```plantuml
@startuml lkmSasanga_fas-web-app
autonumber

actor User

participant "App.js\n(Root Component)" as App
participant "Login Component" as Login
participant "InputControl Component" as InputControl
participant "RequestData Component" as RequestData
participant "API\n(Backend)" as API
participant "Dashboard Component" as Dashboard
participant "Firebase Hosting" as Firebase

User -> App: Open Application
App -> Login: Render Login UI
Login -> App: User Logs In
App -> InputControl: Navigate to InputControl
InputControl -> RequestData: Submit Search Query
RequestData -> API: Fetch Sentiment Data
API -> RequestData: Return Sentiment Data
RequestData -> Dashboard: Pass Data for Visualization
Dashboard -> User: Display Sentiment Visualization

activate Firebase
App -> Firebase: Deploy Application
Firebase -> App: Serve Application
deactivate Firebase

@enduml
```